@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nneelx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v2 + wp.cos((v2 + 0.90 + v2 + 0.25)))
    v1 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.57 + v1 + 0.69)) - tmp)
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.49 - v0 + 0.10)) + 0.40)
    tmp = 0.81
    v1 = wp.exp((tmp / (v1 + 0.20 + v1 + 0.00)))
    data[tid] = v0
